yanide deaths but never mentioned harming her husband. Asked whether Mrs. <PERSON> Nickell </PERSON> had indicated an intent to kill, Ms. <PERSON> Stewart </PERSON> replied, `` Absolutely not. Not ever.'' Prosecutors say the <PERSON> Nickells </PERSON>' marriage was unhappy, and that Mrs. <PERSON> Nickell </PERSON> was determined not to lose her trailer home in a divorce. Witnesses have testified that the <PERSON> Nickells </PERSON> were several thousand dollars in debt when <PERSON> Nickell </PERSON> died.
